-- Barclays Said to Plan Covered Bond Sales in Pounds
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2012-01-04T17:35:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-04/barclays-said-to-plan-covered-bond-sales-in-pounds.html
Barclays Plc (BARC)  plans to sell covered
bonds in pounds, according to a banker involved in the
transaction.  The bank hired Citigroup Inc., Lloyds Banking Group Plc and
 Banco Santander SA (SAN)  to manage the deal with Barclays, the banker
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Martin at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net  